
Client 
------------
crontab.client - Client side crontab file
ddns_client.sh - Client side script.  Place in /usr/local/bin


Server
-------------
ddns.conf      - Apache config file.  Place in /etc/httpd/conf.d
ddns_init      - Place in /etc/init.d to start application
ddns_server.sh - Place in /home/ddns/apps/DDNS/ddns-bin.  This shell script 
                   does everything
application    - This is the Dancer app.  It accepts a request, validates it againts
                   the database and launches the above shell script.
ddns.sql       - ddns table


